%% Diagram: Spanner TrueTime Commit Wait
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Leader as Spanner Leader
    participant TT as TrueTime
    participant Replicas

    Client->>Leader: Begin transaction
    Leader->>Replicas: Acquire locks (Paxos)
    Leader->>TT: TT.now() returns [earliest, latest]
    Note over Leader: Pick s = TT.now().latest
    Leader->>Replicas: Replicate write at timestamp s
    Replicas-->>Leader: Quorum ack
    Note over Leader: Commit wait — block until\nTT.now().earliest > s\n(typically ~2 epsilon, 8-14 ms)
    Leader-->>Client: Commit ack
    Note over Client,Replicas: External consistency: any later\ntransaction observes T1's effects
